caption.p: ZIKV neutralising capacity assessment. The figure shows the titer of ZIKV-neutralising antibodies that was evaluated in sera of mice vaccinated with only EDIII protein, CuMVtt-EDIII and CuMVtt-EDIII plus DOPS. The data shown here are from samples collected on days 21, 42 and 63 and two independent experiments were performed. Note: ** p < 0.001, *** p < 0.0001.
